{"tid":1379321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【 39秒冇成本救港方法！！！】","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T01:02:56.000Z","uid":292733,"like":146,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"d037f9b0d0bcd4f6f44dab792bb0e5148b2d3059","tid":1379321,"uid":292733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:39:09.000Z","msg":"面對住藍絲 唔明佢地點解好似比人洗左腦咁 盲撐中國/政府/警察？<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點解 <br />\n<br />\n但係其實我地有野可以做到架！<br />\n就係截斷佢地吸收洗腦資訊既途徑！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 去藍絲Facebook page㩒report<br />\n搵左幾個好熱門既page比大家 一睇d follow,個個post有幾千like同share拍得住連登熱門正皮 comment既人多到嚇死人<br />\n<br />\n。幫港出聲Silent Majority<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilentmajorityhk%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=578e04b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n。港人講地<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/speakouthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fspeakouthk%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=8616b675\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/speakouthk/</a><br />\n<br />\n。我們支持屈穎妍小姐繼續為香港人發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/We.Support.Chris.Wat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWe.Support.Chris.Wat%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=481506f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/We.Support.Chris.Wat/</a><br />\n<br />\n。保普選 反佔中 港人揮手區<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Anti.OCLP928/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAnti.OCLP928%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=df8f0cbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Anti.OCLP928/</a><br />\n<br />\n。向香港警察致敬<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSaluteToHKPolice%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=0040e753\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/</a><br />\n<br />\n。撐警大聯盟<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-800448983322897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-800448983322897&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=2332c2ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-800448983322897</a>/<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 去鄉討㩒嬲嬲豬<br />\n成個鄉討都係藍絲大本營 係度圍爐取暖 咁多五毛走黎連登吠 果邊一個post閒閒地一個comment 都百幾個心心眼<br />\n人係群體動物 最驚自己係少數 會唔敢出聲<br />\n<br />\n3. 幫藍絲Block Facebook page同Follow<br />\n可以用到佢地手機/ac既話<br />\n先Report再Block曬上面講果堆page<br />\n然後Follow Sing Majority呢d page放低佢地戒心"},{"pid":"da160776a52d85cd342efb443c8c8eabab2c406d","tid":1379321,"uid":292733,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:44:54.000Z","msg":"義士係出面食彈 我地都好多野可以做！"},{"pid":"4de006c2f69417ae81c3ac95e0ad8a1d8d27ae32","tid":1379321,"uid":292733,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3XmaiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3XmaiA.png&h=6f15021b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y66x1qi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy66x1qi.png&h=db3e6763&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsMFqRZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsMFqRZ.png&h=79a37bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLtHEb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLtHEb1.png&h=3915a414&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbecb629aab3c98a19f91a57bf02067435012147","tid":1379321,"uid":92653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"